  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "2. In a small bowl, mix together olive oil, Italian seasoning, minced garlic, and chopped parsley.",
    "3. Brush the mixture evenly onto the chicken breast.",
    "4. Bake the chicken in the preheated oven for 20-25 minutes, or until cooked through.",
    "5. While the chicken is baking, warm the wrap in the oven for 2-3 minutes.",
    "6. Once the chicken is done, slice it thinly.",
    "7. Assemble the wrap by spreading shredded mozzarella cheese on the wrap, followed by sliced chicken, and topped with chopped fresh basil.",
    "8. Serve immediately and enjoy!"
